        {
            "title": "美元指數連升4交易日　勞動力市場穩固",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美元靠穩，數據顯示美國勞動力市場穩固，為聯儲局短期內維持利率不變提供空間。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美元\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/2024619_GL_FB_US-dollar_source-licensed_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美元\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/2024619_GL_FB_US-dollar_source-licensed_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美元</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在紐約尾市，美元指數在97.9附近，升幅約0.2%，連升4個交易日。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐元兌美元跌0.1%，報1.1768美元。之前有報道指，歐洲央行總裁拉加德預計將在8年任期結束之前離職。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英鎊兌美元跌約0.3%，報1.3456美元。美元兌日圓升0.1%，報155.04日圓。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美國上星期首次申領失業救濟人數減少2.3萬人，跌至20.6萬人，低於預期的22.5萬人。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">明尼亞波利斯聯儲銀行總裁卡什卡利表示，勞動力市場仍相當強韌，聯儲局已接近實現充分就業和穩定物價兩大目標。利率期貨顯示，市場預計聯儲局6月會議前最少減息0.25厘的機會低於一半。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15672999-%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e6%8c%87%e6%95%b8%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%874%e4%ba%a4%e6%98%93%e6%97%a5%e3%80%80%e5%8b%9e%e5%8b%95%e5%8a%9b%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4%e7%a9%a9%e5%9b%ba",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20240410_source-licensed_USD_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-20 08:26:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "金價在5000美元關口爭持",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">金價在每盎司5000美元關口爭持，投資者正評估美伊緊張局勢，而美國上周首次申領失業救濟人數減少，亦預示勞動力市場趨穩。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">現貨金較早時報5000.16美元，升幅0.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紐約4月期金收市報4997.4美元，跌幅0.2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15672991-%e9%87%91%e5%83%b9%e5%9c%a85000%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e9%97%9c%e5%8f%a3%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240917_PL_gold_source-licensed_1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-20 08:26:45",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "油價升近2%　美伊緊張局勢升級",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際油價收市升近2%，創逾6個半月高位收市。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"油價\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Oil_source-ap_-1-1-2-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"油價\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Oil_source-ap_-1-1-2-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">油價</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紐約期油收報每桶66.43美元，升1.24美元，升幅1.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">倫敦布蘭特期油收市報每桶71.66美元，升1.31美元，升幅近1.9%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">市場憂慮美國與伊朗緊張局勢升級，兩國在中東產油區加強軍事活動。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15672993-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%912%e3%80%80%e7%be%8e%e4%bc%8a%e7%b7%8a%e5%bc%b5%e5%b1%80%e5%8b%a2%e5%8d%87%e7%b4%9a",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/Oil.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-20 08:26:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐股收市下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐洲主要股市收市下跌，英法股市自上日紀錄高位回落。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英國富時100指數報10627點，跌59點，跌幅近0.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">法國CAC指數報8398點，跌30點，跌幅近0.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德國DAX指數報25043點，跌234點，跌幅0.9%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15672986-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%e4%b8%8b%e8%b7%8c-21",
